# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# JesAI — Bangladesh Legal Literacy AI
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── SUPABASE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Required. Get these from your Supabase project dashboard:
#   https://app.supabase.com → your project → Settings → API
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ values are exposed to the browser.
# SERVICE_ROLE_KEY is server-only — never expose it to the client.

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL="https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co"
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY="eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY="eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."

# ── APP URL ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Used for password-reset redirect links.
# Update to your production URL after deploying.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL="http://localhost:3000"

# ── AI / LLM ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Google Gemini (free tier available at https://aistudio.google.com)
# Leave empty to fall back to the static knowledge store.
GEMINI_API_KEY=""

# ── PAYMENT (bKash / Nagad display numbers) ───────────────────
NEXT_PUBLIC_BKASH_NUMBER=""
NEXT_PUBLIC_NAGAD_NUMBER=""

# ── CONTACT ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# WhatsApp number shown in paywall messages (e.g. 01712345678)
NEXT_PUBLIC_WHATSAPP_NUMBER=""
